In [7]:
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(10,3), dpi=100)
ax1,ax2=fig.subplots(1,2)

m1=3
s1=5
data=np.random.normal(m1,s1,size=10000)

_=ax1.hist(data, bins=30, edgecolor='k')
_=ax1.set_xticks([m1-s1, m1, m1+s1], [m1-s1, m1, m1+s1], fontsize=16)
_=ax1.set_xlabel('xlabel', fontsize=20)

_=ax2.hist(data, bins=30, edgecolor='k')
_=ax2.set_xticks([m1], ['$\\mu$={}'.format(m1)], fontsize=16)
_=ax2.set_xlabel('xlabel', fontsize=20)

_=ax1.tick_params(axis='both',
                  direction='inout',
                  width=5,
                  length=10,
                  color='c')

_=ax2.tick_params(axis='x',
                  direction='out',
                  width=5, 
                  length=10, 
                  pad=20,
                  color='y',
                  labelcolor='g',labelsize=30)

_=ax2.tick_params(axis='y',
                  direction='in',
                  width=2, length=20, 
                  pad=10,
                  color='r',
                  labelcolor='b',
                  labelsize=15)

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(10,5), dpi=100)
axs=fig.subplots(1,2)

d1=pd.read_table('data/11w_d3.txt', index_col=0, sep='\t')
d1

## axs[0], scatter 함수 한번 호출
_=axs[0].scatter(d1['x'],d1['y'])
for ind, x, y in zip(d1.index, d1['x'], d1['y']):
    _=axs[0].text(x,y-0.2,ind, ha='center',va='top', fontsize=15)
    
_=axs[0].set_xlim(-1,6)
_=axs[0].set_ylim(-1,6)

## axs[1], scatter 함수 각 점의 수만큼 호출
for ind, x, y in zip(d1.index, d1['x'], d1['y']):
    _=axs[1].scatter(x,y, color='b')
    _=axs[1].text(x,y-0.2,ind, ha='center',va='top', fontsize=15)
    
_=axs[1].set_xlim(-1,6)
_=axs[1].set_ylim(-1,6)

In [48]:
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(5,3), dpi=150)
ax=fig.subplots()

def pdf(X, mu, sigma):
    a = 1/(sigma * np.sqrt(2*np.pi))
    b = -1/(2*(sigma**2))
    return a * np.exp(b * ((X - mu)** 2))

m1=1
s1=2

X = np.linspace(m1-5, m1+5, 1000)
_=ax.plot(X, pdf(X, m1, s1), color = 'k')

_=ax.set_xticks([m1],labels=['$\\mu$={}'.format(m1)], fontsize=16)

In [54]:
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(7,4), dpi=100)
ax1=fig.subplots()

X=np.linspace(0,2*np.pi, 100)
Y1=np.sin(X)
Y2=np.cos(X)
Y3=np.random.uniform(-1,1,size=100)

_=ax1.plot(X,Y1, c='k', lw=3, ls='--',label='sin(x)')
_=ax1.plot(X,Y2, c='r', lw=1, ls=':',label='cos(x)')
_=ax1.scatter(X,Y3, marker='*', label='Star')
_=ax1.legend(title='plot & scatter',fontsize=13, title_fontsize=16)

## ax2 (method2)
l1=ax2.plot(X,Y1, c='k', lw=3, ls='--')

legend의 parameter로 label을 사용하는 경우 (plot, scatter)¶

In [68]:
fig=plt.figure(figsize=(13,4), dpi=100)
ax1, ax2=fig.subplots(1,2)

X=np.linspace(0,2*np.pi, 100)
Y1=np.sin(X)
Y2=np.cos(X)
Y3=np.random.uniform(-1,1,size=100)

## ax1
_=ax1.plot(X,Y1, c='k', lw=3, ls='--',label='sin(x)')
_=ax1.plot(X,Y2, c='r', lw=1, ls=':',label='cos(x)')
_=ax1.scatter(X,Y3, marker='*', label='Star')
_=ax1.legend(title='plot & scatter',fontsize=13, title_fontsize=16)

## ax2
plot1=ax2.plot(X,Y1, c='k', lw=3, ls='--')
plot2=ax2.plot(X,Y2, c='r', lw=1, ls=':')
scat1=ax2.scatter(X,np.random.uniform(-1,1,100), marker='*')
plot2[0]
scat1

_=ax2.legend(handles=(plot1[0], plot2[0], scat1), labels=('sin(x)', 'cos(x)', 'Star'),
             title='plot & scatter',fontsize=13, title_fontsize=16)

# 10이상인 값에 대해서만 bar위에 해당 y값을 text로 넣으시오

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(8,3), dpi=100)
ax=fig.subplots()

X=np.arange(15)
Y=np.random.randint(5,15,15)
Y
_=ax.bar(X, Y)

#=== 코드작성 ===#
for x, y in zip(X,Y):
    if y>=10:
        _=ax.text(x,y,'{}'.format(y), ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=16)
#=== 코드작성 끝 ===#

_=ax.axhline(10, color='r', linestyle=':')
_=ax.set_ylim(0,17)

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(5,3), dpi=150)
ax=fig.subplots()

def pdf(X, mu, sigma):
    a = 1/(sigma * np.sqrt(2*np.pi))
    b = -1/(2*(sigma**2))
    return a * np.exp(b * ((X - mu)** 2))

m1=1
s1=2

X = np.linspace(m1-5, m1+5, 1000)
_=ax.plot(X, pdf(X, m1, s1), color = 'k')

_=ax.set_xticks([m1],labels=['$\\mu$={}'.format(m1)], fontsize=16)

## 코드작성
m0=m1-2
m2=m1+2

y0=pdf(m0, m1, s1)
y2=pdf(m2, m1, s1)

ax.plot([m0,m2],[y0,y2])
ax.text(m1,y0, "$\\sigma={}$".format(s1), ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=15)

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(4,4), dpi=100)
ax=fig.subplots()

# scatter x,y
d1=np.random.uniform(0,1,size=(500,2))
df1=pd.DataFrame(d1, columns=['x','y'])
_=ax.scatter(df1['x'],df1['y'], edgecolor='k')

# s1=x+y
df1['s1']=df1['x']+df1['y']

## 코드작성
df2=df1.sort_values(by='s1')
mx, my=df2.iloc[-1].loc[['x', 'y']]
nx, ny=df2.iloc[0].loc[['x', 'y']]

_=ax.scatter([mx, nx],[my, ny], color='r')

_=ax.text(mx,my,'max',ha='left',va='bottom', fontsize=14)
_=ax.text(nx,ny,'min',ha='right',va='top', fontsize=14)

## 코드작성 끝

_=ax.set_xlim(-0.2,1.2)
_=ax.set_ylim(-0.2,1.2)
